Victor Travers https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victor_Travers 0 Victor Travers (1884 – 26 May 1948) was an English character actor of theatre and film, known for his work in many of the Three Stooges films. During his career, which began in 1938 and ended with his death in 1948, he appeared in more than 80 films.
